ore_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-09 13:37", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我目前把剩下10%全打了金融 我去帮市场突破<br/>这次不用你们了  怕你们死。<br/>毕竟你们都没挣钱", "lou": 742, "content_length": 79, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770615458}, {"pid": 857557474, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 50, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-09 13:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857557215,45974302,1343]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=63733883]KawnManhung[/uid] (2026-02-09 13:40):[/b]<br/><br/>我再建议一次楼里的xdm，从去年9.18开始，我就认为任何楼里小微散去冲金融助力关键点位基本上没有任何好处，比这个坏的只有一个就是追高<br/>我个人认为没什么意义，打赢了去对的方向就好<br/>输了还要被套，何苦呢？<br/>如果看红警08的，就知道一句台词“你看这个小X，东惹一下西惹一下，他以为他是我”[/quote]<br/>我好歹不算小资金 就该为市场做点贡献。 市场好了 什么都能补涨  市场不好 做全对才能挣钱。", "lou": 743, "content_length": 85, "reply_to": 857557215, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770615783}, {"pid": 857558004, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-09 13:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857557573,45974302,1343]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65329649]zippo578[/uid] (2026-02-09 13:43):[/b]<br/><br/>你们都没抓住重点<br/>狼大意思是<br/>“我满仓了”[/quote]<br/>我能T出去 至少能T回70%", "lou": 744, "content_length": 26, "reply_to": 857557573, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770616055}, {"pid": 857560075, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 44, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-09 14:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857559529,45974302,1347]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-02-09 14:00):[/b]<br/><br/>这个位置斗争好激烈，这就是关键点位的意义么[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>4117以下  和维持4117以上是两个维度 很难和你们解释", "lou": 745, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 857559529, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770617078}, {"pid": 857562215, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 55, "scor